{"tid":1084187,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【鐵探】慨嘆無緣與影后惠英紅演對手戲　蔡思貝：覺得自己好不幸","createTime":"2019-03-30T08:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T05:23:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ecda49c1e52438078d6cd28b8a015062ebac32d6","tid":1084187,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"蔡思貝今日（29/3）出席無綫重頭劇《鐵探》記者會，思貝透露這個角色內心戲好重：「因為講呢個女仔有創傷後遺症，細個差啲俾人強姦，被人綁架困咗喺個棺材入面成個星期，然之後佢點樣出返嚟做事，最後佢竟然選擇做警察，雖然佢有坎坷遭遇，但仍堅強面對自己嘅人生，所以我覺得係一個好勵志嘅角色，最後佢會面對返呢個陰影。」<br />\n無綫重頭劇《鐵探》由蘇萬聰監製打造出電影感重的劇集，更找來影后惠英紅、姜皓文助陣。思貝遺憾表示：「其實我好不幸，因為我同黑仔同紅姐好少戲，初頭收到劇本，通知要拍嘅時候，非常期待，仲心諗可以同紅姐做對手戲，後尾知道原來係多群戲，所以都覺好可惜，惟有等下一次再拍《鐵探2》或者電影版，再同佢哋兩個合作，拍更多嘅戲。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2614610/org/3dff704c16ad1f04504746fa3e91ca28.jpg/3aJoXwXNyqDMqc59Kez99H_e2OLzPF72UBNcf3oTXH8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2614610%2Forg%2F3dff704c16ad1f04504746fa3e91ca28.jpg%2F3aJoXwXNyqDMqc59Kez99H_e2OLzPF72UBNcf3oTXH8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=4a9e1bf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_cENVotW0j0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_cENVotW0j0&d=Ru8OiKpQtXbNv5YRwinC6hQ2JDI1%2B2PXXyGzAukhOpM%3D&h=cc224a3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_cENVotW0j0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/312280/%E9%90%B5%E6%8E%A2-%E6%85%A8%E5%98%86%E7%84%A1%E7%B7%A3%E8%88%87%E5%BD%B1%E5%90%8E%E6%83%A0%E8%8B%B1%E7%B4%85%E6%BC%94%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%88%B2-%E8%94%A1%E6%80%9D%E8%B2%9D-%E8%A6%BA%E5%BE%97%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%8D%E5%B9%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F312280%2F%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%258E%25A2-%25E6%2585%25A8%25E5%2598%2586%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B7%25A3%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%2590%258E%25E6%2583%